---

---

<section class="capture-section py-0 md:py-0 relative z-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2
            class="font-medium mb-6 text-[32px] md:text-[48px] animate-on-scroll"
            style="font-family: 'Paralucent', sans-serif; color:#E8EBF0; line-height:1.05;"
        >
            Como uma <span style="color:#E8EBF0; font-weight:800"
                >Página de Alto Padrão</span
            > pode te ajudar a ter mais resultados
        </h2>

        <p
            class="mb-10 animate-on-scroll delay-100"
            style="font-family: 'Paralucent', sans-serif; color:#ABAEB4; font-size:16px; md:font-size:18px; max-width:900px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto;"
        >
            Quando o seu lead acessa a sua página para se inscrever no seu
            evento, ou comprar seu produto, essa página precisa refletir
            fielmente a premissa da sua oferta. Caso contrário, ela não vai
            trazer credibilidade e você pode perder o lead e gastar mais com
            tráfego.
        </p>

        <div
            class="relative group w-[300px] md:w-[380px] h-[65px] md:h-[75px] mx-auto cursor-pointer z-10 animate-on-scroll delay-200"
        >
            <div
                class="absolute -inset-10 rounded-full bg-white/20 opacity-0 blur-3xl transition-opacity duration-500 group-hover:opacity-100"
            >
            </div>
            <div
                class="flash-overlay absolute inset-0 rounded-full bg-white pointer-events-none z-20 mix-blend-overlay"
            >
            </div>
            <div
                class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full overflow-hidden p-[1.5px] bg-[#5C666F]"
            >
                <div
                    class="conic-spinner absolute inset-[-100%] w-[300%] h-[300%] left-[-100%] top-[-100%]"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="h-full w-full bg-[#0F1115] rounded-full relative z-10"
                >
                </div>
            </div>
            <span
                class="absolute top-0 left-[37.5px] w-[2px] h-[2px] bg-white rounded-full z-20 shadow-[0_0_2px_white]"
            ></span>
            <span
                class="absolute top-0 right-[37.5px] w-[2px] h-[2px] bg-white rounded-full z-20 shadow-[0_0_2px_white]"
            ></span>
            <span
                class="absolute bottom-0 left-[37.5px] w-[2px] h-[2px] bg-white rounded-full z-20 shadow-[0_0_2px_white]"
            ></span>
            <span
                class="absolute bottom-0 right-[37.5px] w-[2px] h-[2px] bg-white rounded-full z-20 shadow-[0_0_2px_white]"
            ></span>

            <a
                href="https://wa.me/5562981752097?text=Ol%C3%A1%2C+gostaria+de+solicitar+um+or%C3%A7amento."
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="absolute inset-0 z-30 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full"
            >
                <span
                    class="tracking-widest font-medium mr-3 md:mr-4 text-[14px] md:text-[18px]"
                    style="font-family: 'Paralucent', sans-serif; color: #E8EBF0;"
                >
                    ENVIAR MENSAGEM
                </span>
                <span
                    class="transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1 group-hover:-translate-y-1"
                >
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        class="w-5 h-5 md:w-[26px] md:h-[26px]"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                    >
                        <path
                            d="M5 19.5L19.5 5"
                            stroke="#9AEBF7"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                        <path
                            d="M9.5 5H19.5V15"
                            stroke="#9AEBF7"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                    </svg>
                </span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
